# 301 redirects for retired URLs from previous versions of the site.
# Goal: pass link equity to the closest live page and clear them out of
# Search Console's "Crawled - currently not indexed" bucket.
#
# Host canonicalization (www -> apex, http -> https) is handled by Netlify's
# primary-domain setting, not here. These are path-only rules.

/about                /             301
/services             /#services    301
/salesforce-services  /#services    301
/legal                /privacy      301
/newsletter           /             301
